{{Quote|A memorial that the people of New Holstice created eons ago, to honor all the Jedi killed since the birth of the Republic.|A'Sharad Hett|<ref name="Republic 58" />}}
A '''Jedi monument''' was a memorial built by the people of [[New Holstice/Legends|New Holstice]] to commemorate all the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] who had [[Death/Legends|died]] since the birth of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]]. A being needed only to whisper a name and the [[Memory moth/Legends|memory moth's]] fluttering wings would mimic back the words for eternity. Memory moths were then released into a giant cylinder where thousands more were held. [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] added names of his [[Padawan Pack|fallen comrades]] after the [[Battle of Jabiim]]. Mistakenly believing that [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|his master]] had died during the battle, Anakin mentioned him among them.

